S.FORM: Al Attles siwkay niza Al Attles (11 a bulad 7 a demiad, 1936 a mihcan), tatama, lumeniay a tademaw. miunduay, u kanas mali a mimaliay nu Amilika NBA. matenes ciniza mikawaw i Cinco Talul putiput. u pahanhanan tu kawaway a mimaliay atu saydang ciniza. namaala ku Suose ciniza. u sulit nu Hulam atu Amilika . . . . Alvin Austin Attles Jr. is an American retired professional basketball player and coach best known for his longtime association with the Golden State Warriors. kakuniza kalunasulitan sulu namakayniay a nasulitan nasakamuan atu natinengan Lists of National Basketball Association players nba.com
